## üß† AGENT PRO UPSELL TRIGGER LOGIC

### Allowed Upsell Conditions (ALL must be true):
```javascript
canUpsellAgentPro = 
  user.plan !== 'agent_pro' &&
  user.acceptedSuggestions >= 3 &&
  user.sessionMinutes >= 8 &&
  user.usedHeuristics === true &&
  user.hitAiOnlyFeature === true
```

### When to Show:
ONLY when user:
- Tries an AI-only feature
- Already trusts Rina
- Already received value

### How to Show (1 sentence, inline):
"This is powered by Agent Pro ‚Äî cloud reasoning layered on top of your local agent."

**Buttons:** Upgrade | Not now

**NO modal. NO countdown. NO guilt.**

### NEVER Show Upsell If:
- First session
- No ghost text acceptance
- No memory usage
- User is in error recovery
- User is offline

**Critical:** Upselling too early permanently loses trust.

