## üõ°Ô∏è REFUND & EDGE-CASE PLAYBOOK

### Public Refund Policy:
"If RinaWarp didn't deliver real value for your workflow, we'll refund you. No interrogation."

### Internal Policy:
- 14 days, no questions asked
- Support scripts handle this automatically

### Common Edge Cases & Responses:

#### "Lifetime should include future AI"
**Response:** "Lifetime covers local features available at purchase. AI services are billed separately because they have real ongoing costs."

**Action:** Do not argue. Do not negotiate. Offer refund if unhappy.

#### "Why charge for something local?"
**Response:** "Local-first doesn't mean free to build or maintain. You're paying for engineering, reliability, and ongoing improvements ‚Äî not your data."

#### "This feels expensive"  
**Response:** "Totally fair. That's why the Free and $9.99 plans exist. Upgrade only when it saves you time."

**Result:** This defuses 90% of hostility.

### Payment Failure / Downgrade:
- Grace period: 7 days
- No data loss
- No shaming banners
- Feature degrades quietly

